title: Bar Taco
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Organic, Raw, Delivery, Take-out, Mexican, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bar Taco is a franchise chain restaurant that goes to great lengths to satisfy all dietary preferences. The grill and fryer that they use for vegan items is separate from the ones they use for animal products. Multiple vegan choices. Gluten Free, nut allergy sensitive, raw and cooked.
